---
// Componente: Cómo Funciona / Pasos del Proceso
---

<section class="py-16 sm:py-20 lg:py-28 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 bg-white">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
    <!-- Section Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-12 sm:mb-16">
      <span class="text-xs sm:text-sm font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase text-detalles-teal">Proceso Simple</span>
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-display font-bold text-gray-900 mt-4">
        Cómo Trabajamos Contigo
      </h2>
    </div>

    <!-- Steps Grid -->
    <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8 lg:gap-6">
      <!-- Paso 1 -->
      <div class="relative group">
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white text-2xl font-bold mb-6 shadow-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-detalles-teal to-detalles-teal-dark group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
            1
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-display font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Consulta Inicial</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Contáctanos y cuéntanos sobre tu evento. Definimos tus necesidades y preferencias.
          </p>
        </div>
        <!-- Connector Line (hidden on mobile, shown on lg) -->
        <div class="hidden lg:block absolute top-10 left-full w-full h-0.5 -translate-x-1/2 bg-gradient-to-r from-detalles-teal/50 to-transparent"></div>
      </div>

      <!-- Paso 2 -->
      <div class="relative group">
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white text-2xl font-bold mb-6 shadow-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-detalles-teal to-detalles-teal-dark group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
            2
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-display font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Cotización</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Creamos una propuesta personalizada con precios transparentes y sin sorpresas.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="hidden lg:block absolute top-10 left-full w-full h-0.5 -translate-x-1/2 bg-gradient-to-r from-detalles-teal/50 to-transparent"></div>
      </div>

      <!-- Paso 3 -->
      <div class="relative group">
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white text-2xl font-bold mb-6 shadow-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-detalles-teal to-detalles-teal-dark group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
            3
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-display font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Reserva</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Confirma tu fecha y separamos todo el mobiliario y decoración que necesitas.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="hidden lg:block absolute top-10 left-full w-full h-0.5 -translate-x-1/2 bg-gradient-to-r from-detalles-teal/50 to-transparent"></div>
      </div>

      <!-- Paso 4 -->
      <div class="relative group">
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white text-2xl font-bold mb-6 shadow-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-detalles-teal to-detalles-teal-dark group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
            4
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-display font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Entrega y Montaje</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Llevamos todo a tu evento, lo instalamos y recogemos cuando termines.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <div class="mt-12 sm:mt-16 text-center">
      <a 
        href="/cotizacion" 
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 px-8 sm:px-10 py-4 sm:py-5 rounded-full text-white text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-2xl hover:scale-105 bg-gradient-to-r from-detalles-teal to-detalles-teal-dark focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-detalles-teal focus:ring-offset-2"
      >
        Solicita tu Cotización
        <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6"/>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>